Japan Lifts Atomic Alert to Highest Level, Matching Chernobyl

-- B y   K y u n g   B o k   C h o
-- 
2011-04-12T02:04:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-12/japan-lifts-atomic-alert-to-highest-level-matching-chernobyl.html
Japan ’s nuclear safety agency
raised the severity rating of the crisis at the Fukushima Dai-
Ichi nuclear plant to the highest level.  Japan’s Nuclear and Industrial Safety Agency lifted the
rating level to 7, from 5, an agency official said today in a
televised briefing.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
